<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Acts of racism</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Institutional_racism" title="Institutional racism">Institutional racism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/State_racism" title="State racism">State racism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Racial_profiling" title="Racial profiling">Racial profiling</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Racism_by_country" title="Racism by country">Racism by country</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hate_speech" title="Hate speech">Hate speech</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Racial_segregation" title="Racial segregation">Racial segregation</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Stereotype" title="Stereotype">Stereotype</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Scientific_racism" title="Scientific racism">Scientific racism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Slavery" title="Slavery">Slavery</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Crime_of_apartheid" title="Crime of apartheid">Crime of apartheid</a></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Racial violence</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-even">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Ethnic_cleansing" title="Ethnic cleansing">Ethnic cleansing</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hate_crime" title="Hate crime">Hate crime</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Race_war" title="Race war">Race war</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Genocide" title="Genocide">Genocide</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Lynching" title="Lynching">Lynching</a></div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr style="height:2px">
<td></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="navbox-group" style=";;">Racism against groups</td>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left:2px solid #fdfdfd;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em"><a href="/wiki/Stereotypes_of_Native_Americans" title="Stereotypes of Native Americans">Native Americans</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Arabism" title="Anti-Arabism">Arabs</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Armenianism" title="Anti-Armenianism">Armenians</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Stereotypes_of_blacks" title="Stereotypes of blacks" class="mw-redirect">Blacks</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Sinophobia" title="Sinophobia">Chinese</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Hispanophobia" title="Hispanophobia">Hispanics</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Irish_racism" title="Anti-Irish racism">Irish</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Italianism" title="Anti-Italianism">Italians</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Japanese_sentiment" title="Anti-Japanese sentiment">Japanese</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Antisemitism" title="Antisemitism">Jews</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Mexican_sentiment" title="Anti-Mexican sentiment">Mexicans</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Anti-Polish_sentiment" title="Anti-Polish sentiment">Poles</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Antiziganism" title="Antiziganism">Roma people</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Russophobia" title="Russophobia" class="mw-redirect">Russians</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Indophobia" title="Indophobia">South Asians</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Stereotypes_of_East_and_Southeast_Asians_in_the_United_States" title="Stereotypes of East and Southeast Asians in the United States">East Asians</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Stereotypes_of_white_people" title="Stereotypes of white people">Whites</a></div>
